name: So Long and Thanks for all the Phish
description:
"So Long and Thanks for all the Phish" is a nod to our creative forebears and noodlers of yore. Minted to celebrate 600K objkts it is our first NFT available for sale. It is also the first of a series of works released as part of our upcoming exhibition "Counterpoise[Fish out of Water]" at Bert Green Fine Art in Chicago, IL, that opens January 15th, omicron willing. Keep an eye out on our twitter feed for more deets @happyR3turns
